title: Bartosz Broniszewski
text: Bartosz Broniszewski (born 23 January 1988 in <a href="Munich">Munich</a>) is a German <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> of Polish origin, who plays for <a href="SC%20Pfullendorf">SC Pfullendorf</a>.
